{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":"Miguel de Guzman","homeCity":"Bulacan, Philippines"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/2534d/donaldtrump.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 76.72327672327673%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"donaldtrump\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/f8fb9/donaldtrump.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/e8976/donaldtrump.jpg 148w,\n/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/63df2/donaldtrump.jpg 295w,\n/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/f8fb9/donaldtrump.jpg 590w,\n/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/85e3d/donaldtrump.jpg 885w,\n/static/5c6d0167ea0fb5c596929130e4a41761/2534d/donaldtrump.jpg 1001w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Wherever you live in this world, Donald Trump has affected your life in a way, mostly bad in my opinion.</p>\n<p>I have a lot of things to say about how Donald Trump continue to impact the world. Let’s start with the bad stuff:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>The power of social and mainstream media.</b> His election inarguably was won through his marketing skills (He’s great at it to be honest), maintream media kept highlighting all of the stupid things that he say all day - non-stop. That is crazy to think that he got around 2 billion dollars worth of free publicity through his rethorics. Social media magnified the problem through its ability to consume the people’s attention 24/7. This a big hole in the way majority of us view the world as we forgot how to think and analyze what is truly beneficial to talk about.. Another example why I keep saying most people are like zombies nowadays. </li>\n<li>Climate Change Denial.</li>\n<li>Lying becomes the new normal.</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Wherever you live in this world, Donald Trump has affected your life in a way, mostly bad in my opinion. I have a lot of things to say about…","fields":{"tagSlugs":["/tags/creating-art/","/tags/talking-history/","/tags/talking-homosapiens/","/tags/blog/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"The Donald Trump Effect","tags":["creating-art","talking-history","talking-homosapiens","blog"],"date":"March 15, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/the-donald-trump-effect/"}}